w\" | \"Party People (Ignite the World)\"\n| Mikey Minden\n|-\n| 2013\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Get It Tonight\" <small>(featuring Flo Rida)</small>\n| Steven Johnson\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2014\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Painkillr\" \n| rowspan=\"5\" | Mikey Minden\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"You Make Me Wanna Dance\" \n|-\n| 2015\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Crazy\" <small>(featuring Maino)</small>\n|-\n| 2016\n! scope=\"row\" | \"How Many Fucks\"\n|-\n| 2017\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Xxpensive\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2019\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Drip\" <small>(Brooke Candy featuring Erika Jayne)</small>\n| Brooke Candy & Angelo Kritikos\n|-\n|}\n\n== Filmography ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |Television and film roles\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"background:#ccc;\" |Year\n! style=\"background:#ccc;\" |Title\n! style=\"background:#ccc;\" |Role\n! style=\"background:#ccc;\" |Notes\n|-\n|1990\u20131991\n|''[[Law & Order]]''\n|Suzanne Morton\n|Episodes: \"Prescription for Death\", \"Violence of Summer\"\n|-\n|1995\n|''Alchemy''\n|Kitty\n|Television film\n|-\n|1996\n|''Lowball''\n|Kate\n|Credited as Erika Chahoy\n|-\n|1997\n|''[[High Incident]]''\n|Cindy Butterworth\n|Episode: \"Remote Control\"\n|-\n|2015\u2013present\n|''[[The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills]]''\n|Herself\n|Main cast member (Season 6\u2013present)\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[Tanked]]''\n|Herself\n|Episode: \"[[Tanked#Season 11 (2016)|Real Aquariums of Beverly Hills]]\"\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[Bravo (U.S. TV network)|The Bravos]]''\n|Herself\n|Musical guest; July 20, 2016<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/the-bravos/954863/|title=The Bravos {{!}} TV Guide|website=TVGuide.com|language=en|access-date=2018-09-21}}</ref>\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[Sharknado: The 4th Awakens]]''\n|Tech Frances\n|Television film\n|-\n|2016\u20132018\n|''[[The Young and the Restless]]''\n|Farrah Dubose\n|Recurring role; 4 episodes\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Fashion Police]]''\n|Herself\n|Episode: \"[[Primetime Emmy Award|The 2017 Primetime Emmy Awards]]\"\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Live from the Red Carpet]]''\n|Herself\n|Episode: \"[[59th Annual Grammy Awards|The 2017 Grammy Awards]]\"\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[American Music Awards of 2017|American Music Awards Red Carpet Live]]''\n|Herself\n|TV Special; Host\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Dancing with the Stars (U.S. TV series)|Dancing with the Stars]]''\n|Herself\n|Contestant; 5 episodes\n|-\n|2018\n|''[[Lip Sync Battle]]''\n|Herself\n|Episode: \"[[Christina Aguilera]] Tribute\"\n|-\n|2018\n|''[[Dish Nation]]''\n|Herself\n|Episode: \"Episode #6.131\"\n|-\n|2018\n|[[Hollywood Medium With Tyler Henry|''Hollywood Medium'']]\n|Herself\n|Episode: \"Erika Jayne, K. Michelle, Rick Fox, Padma Lakshmi\"\n|-\n|2018\n|[[Billboard Music Award|''Billboard Music Awards Red Carpet Live'']]\n|Herself\n| rowspan=\"2\" |TV Special; Host\n|-\n|2018\n|''[[American Music Awards|American Music Awards Red Carpet Live]]''\n|Herself\n|-\n|2018\n|''[[Hit the Floor (TV series)|Hit the Floor]]''\n|Beverly\n|Episode: \"Hot Streak\"\n|-\n|2019\n|''Camp Confessions''\n|Herself\n|Episode: \"Drive-Thru Porn\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |Other productions\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"background:#ccc;\" |Year\n! style=\"background:#ccc;\" |Title\n! style=\"background:#ccc;\" |Production\n! style=\"background:#ccc;\" |Notes\n|-\n|2016\n|Real Housewives in Wonderland\n|[[Bravo (U.S. TV network)|Bravo]]\n|Short film promoting the film ''[[Alice Through the Looking Glass (2016 film)|Alice Through The Looking Glass]]''\n|-\n|2017\n|Too Faced Better Than Sex Mascara \u2013 Starring Erika Jayne<ref>{{Citation|last=toofacedcosmetics|title=Too Faced Better Than Sex Mascara \u2013 Starring Erika Jayne|date=2017-10-19|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VLJJU92FoHs|access-date=2018-07-04}}</ref>\n|Too Faced Cosmetics\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Advertisement\n|-\n|2017\n|The BeautyBlender Swirl Starring Erika Jayne<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.