oo! News Philippines |publisher=SunStar |date=March 29, 2020 |language=en-PH}}</ref>\n**''[[Lapu-Lapu, Cebu|Lapu-Lapu]]''<ref name=\"YahooPHNews-CovidCebuCity\" />\n**''[[Mandaue]]''<ref name=\"CNNPH-CovidMandaue\">{{cite news |title=COVID-19 reaches Cebu as Mandaue City confirms first case |url=http://www.cnnphilippines.com/regional/2020/3/18/Cebu-Mandaue-City-COVID-19-coronavirus.html |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=CNN Philippines |date=March 18, 2020 |language=en}}</ref><ref name=\"YahooPHNews-CovidCebuCity\" />\n**[[Negros Oriental]]<ref name=\"MB-CovidNegrosOr\">{{cite news |last1=Masculino |first1=Glazyl |title=1 positive case of COVID-19 reported in Negros Oriental |url=https://news.mb.com.ph/2020/03/12/1-positive-case-of-covid-19-reported-in-negros-oriental/ |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=Manila Bulletin |date=March 12, 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Eastern Visayas]] (Region VIII)\n**[[Leyte]]<ref name=\"PNAGovPH-CovidLeyte\">{{cite news |last1=Meniano |first1=Sarwell |title=DOH confirms first Covid-19 case in Eastern Visayas |url=https://www.pna.gov.ph/articles/1097553 |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=Philippine News Agency |date=March 23, 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n**[[Northern Samar]]{{citation needed|date=April 2020}}\n**''[[Tacloban]]''{{citation needed|date=April 2020}}\n*[[Zamboanga Peninsula]] (Region IX)\n**''[[Zamboanga City]]''<ref name=\"MB-CovidZamboangaCity\">{{cite news |last1=Lacson |first1=Nonoy |title=First COVID-19 patient confirmed in Zamboanga City |url=https://news.mb.com.ph/2020/03/25/first-covid-19-patient-confirmed-in-zamboanga-city/ |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=Manila Bulletin |date=March 25, 2020}}</ref>\n**[[Zamboanga del Sur]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Zamboanga del Sur reports first two COVID-19 cases |url=https://www.cnnphilippines.com/regional/2020/3/30/Zamboanga-del-Sur-first-coronavirus-cases.html |accessdate=March 30, 2020 |work=CNN Philippine |date=March 30, 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Northern Mindanao]] (Region X)\n**''[[Cagayan de Oro]]''